{"tid":1125668,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"電子支付留證據？傳中國公安大規模傳召涉嫖疑犯","createTime":"2019-04-26T00:36:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T03:06:05.000Z","uid":48083,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"ae65db813c94558a357dfabd24997e419faba6f3","tid":1125668,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T00:36:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rSGwC1x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrSGwC1x.png&h=37f26b89&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZbZx6US.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZbZx6US.png&h=a79cc16d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wXZqHtd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwXZqHtd.png&h=696b05cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eM7zAOd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeM7zAOd.png&h=823277a2&s={SIZE}\" />中國近年大力推行電子支付服務，更有分析指香港應效法中國大陸做法，盡早引入及開發電子支付市場，為市民提供更便利的支付方式。如今，有中國媒體報道指江蘇警方在掃黃行動中，透過電子支付記錄，傳召所有曾在涉事場所花費 600 人民幣以上的人，更指他們都涉嫌嫖娼。事件引起不少反對聲音，亦有律師指當局做法不合乎程序公義。<br />\n<br />\n據中國影音網路《北京時間》引述網民消息指，最近江蘇宜興警方大舉掃黃。而當地警方更在調查支付轉帳記錄後，以短訊形式傳召所有在涉事洗浴中心以電子支付超過 600 元人民幣的市民。在有關短訊中，警方要求他們自動聯絡派出所，並向警方主動供述有關違法行為。更指如果他們沒有正當理由而不接受傳召，執法部門將會上門拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n事件曝光後，引起社會議論紛紛。上海律師丁金坤更在微博上發文表示，當局有關做法不符合程序公義，更指當局做法是「有罪推定」，要求疑犯自證清白，違反法治精神。更建議當局透過大數據分析及查問有關人員，以承擔舉證責任。<br />\n<br />\n而宜興警方則於官方微博上表示，稱網傳「抓獲1200餘名違法人員、掃碼超600元遭傳喚」等說法不實，僅指他們早於 1 月 31 日搗破一個賣淫集團，事件正在調查當中，並指他們會查處造謠者。<br />\n<strong></strong><br />\n<br />\n資料來源：《北京時間》、丁金坤、宜興警方<br />\n<br />\n﻿ &bull; 不想錯過新科技 ? 請 Follow <a href=\"http://unwire.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk&d=fAF%2FER2cs4qp%2F6NYk0BreP4N63GW6AE6v5vQ0jPanwo%3D&h=d0fe0f89\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">unwire.hk</a> FB 專頁<a href=\"http://facebook.com/unwirehk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Funwirehk%2F&d=fAF%2FER2cs4qp%2F6NYk0BreP4N63GW6AE6v5vQ0jPanwo%3D&h=46f01a94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://facebook.com/unwirehk/</a><br />\n&bull; 要入手生活科技潮物 即上 unwire store <br />\n<a href=\"https://store.unwire.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.unwire.hk%2F&d=fAF%2FER2cs4qp%2F6NYk0BreP4N63GW6AE6v5vQ0jPanwo%3D&h=3563236e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://store.unwire.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/04/25/china-police-arresting/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F04%2F25%2Fchina-police-arresting%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=fAF%2FER2cs4qp%2F6NYk0BreP4N63GW6AE6v5vQ0jPanwo%3D&h=c88f4c78\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/04/25/china-police-arresting/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"ab575b32cbcfde0f0d05cab45ab6bb6f40e4a2c6","tid":1125668,"uid":21035,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T00:38:05.000Z","msg":"叫雞都可以用 QR Code 俾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d116a64e1b9b42b0c532e916978a95156562b9b4","tid":1125668,"uid":59283,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T00:40:22.000Z","msg":"香港有幾多支付寶廢中中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86e2735197c90dc9be5bd607178456323eda7391","tid":1125668,"uid":33099,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T00:40:23.000Z","msg":"連續dup 左十粒鐘唔得既 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bf4ac9812c805ef7d66928b257929be85309b99","tid":1125668,"uid":28195,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T00:53:13.000Z","msg":"雷教授近排無出現，唔通已經收到公安通知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9790448a5dc2f80d6f9f43ab00b7ce426e0284c","tid":1125668,"uid":22701,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime"